Quickstrike/Terrorsaur:




Quickstrike leaned on the console, with his head on on his arm. He was 
bored. Whilehe thought of going out and go exploring around the Predacon 
territory, he heard gun shots. He jerked his head up and stood up. He 
listened, then walked to the mouth of the cave. He saw Terrorsaur flying 
low, looking like he was ready to come back in.

"Ah heard some shots!" he said to him. "Go find out what it was."

Terrorsaur grumbled to himself and flew out, turning his course. He picked 
up two signatures on his scanners, one was Predacon. Megatron's Predacon.
